            <td>(not documented &mdash; single-user local design; no per-tenant API surface found)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Zep / Graphiti</strong></td>
            <td>71.2%</td>
            <td>Graphiti: Apache 2.0 &middot; Zep: commercial</td>
