            <td>Yes &mdash; first-party MCP server (Graphiti repo mcp_server/)</td>
            <td>Graphiti: Yes (self-hosted, Docker Compose) &middot; Zep: No (managed SaaS)</td>
            <td>Partial &mdash; Zep cloud (not documented; SaaS account-level isolation assumed) &middot; Graphiti: not documented (build-your-own per README)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="lb-engram-row">
            <td><strong>Engram v0.1.0</strong></td>
